<topic id="eXist-connection-level">
  <title>Actions Available at Connection Level</title>
  <!--Proofed-->
  <body>
    <p>For an eXist database, the actions available at connection level in the <uicontrol>Data
        Source Explorer</uicontrol> view are as follows:</p>
    <dl>
      <dlentry>
        <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/OptionsShortcut16.gif" id="image_mx4_dkt_tr"/>Configure
            Database Sources</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Opens the <uicontrol>Data Sources </uicontrol>
          <xref href="preferences-database.dita">preferences page</xref> where you can configure
          both data sources and connections.</dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry>
        <dt><uicontrol>Disconnect</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Closes the current database connection.</dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry>
        <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Refresh16.png" id="image_pjy_jfw_sr"/>Refresh
          </uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Performs a refresh for the sub-tree of the selected node.</dd>
      </dlentry>
    </dl>
  </body>
</topic>
